                <p></p>
                <p>A personal calendar is provided for every user. To this calender, you can add filters for things like work, class schedules, or any filters you would want.</p>
                <p>To create a new filter, simply click "add filter" button on the "profile" page.
                You can add events to various filters within the calender view by clicking the "+" button with the desired filters selected.</p>
                <p>Filters are a secure way, to let friends, family and coworkers access your daily tasks, filters come with privacy that could be set according to the users needs. </p>

                
                <p>Only users who have been given access the filters will be able to see the events in a specific filter. </p>
               
                <p>Filters are color coded for easy visibility.</p>
                <p>To find friends who use instaCal, just search for them by username/email in the friends tab.</p>
                <p>Follow your favorite celebrities on instaCal! Search for them, follow them and get the latest events on your feed as they share.</p>


